A fleet manager for SlateDB databases

Usage: sleet <COMMAND>

Commands:
  run       Run a fleet node
  status    Show fleet nodes, registered databases, and service placement, derived from the fleet root
  register  Register a database: write its dbs/<db>.toml registry file
  mirror    Mirror operations: sync, restore, prefixes
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
